 in either. Regarding each image through the lens of the discipline that produced it, Elkins simultaneously affirms the unique structure of each way of viewing the world and brings those views together into a vibrant conversation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 7aART / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150361939540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503619395423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781503619395/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles